# Stow Management Standards

## Idempotent Operations

- stow-all.sh must be idempotent; never overwrite non-stow owned files silently
- Back up conflicting files before linking; keep `cursor`/`ghostty` Darwin-only

## Platform-Specific Stowing

- Ghostty and Cursor are stowed only on macOS
